metadata.name: Moon Girl #1/5
metadata.description:
To achieve our dreams, we must confront our fears, overcome difficulties, and not be afraid to take steps forward. Moon Girl overcame her fears by letting go of the balloon in her hand and chasing her dreams. We too must let go of our own balloons and take steps towards our aspirations.

Remember, dreams may seem impossible before they become a reality. However, by believing in ourselves and putting in the work, we can reach our dreams.
